Buenos días Virgilio,

Gracias por compartir tu experiencia con Clicktransfer. Siempre nos ayuda a mejorar nuestra plataforma.

Lamentamos que hayas encontrado problemas a la hora de realizar el pago en la plataforma de Trustly, hemos reportado esta incidencia con ellos y trataran de resolverlo para que no vuelva a suceder en el futuro.

Para responder a tu pregunta, el modo de pago que mas satisface a nuestros clientes es el pago por tarjeta de débito/crédito. 
El pago se concilia de forma instantánea y el dinero se envía de forma mas rápida.

No dudes en contactarnos si te surge cualquier otra duda con tu próximo envío, sera un placer atenderte.

Un cordial saludo,
El equipo Clicktransfer.

companyReply.text:
Dear Carlos,
We are sorry to hear you are disapointed with our service.
To give you further explanation about your case, you have experienced this delay because additional information regarding your auto transfer was needed. 
Indeed, when transferring money to oneself, money transfer companies are obliged by law to request some extra personal data to be able to send your funds between your bank accounts.
We have repeatedly tried to call you to get hold of that information but unfortunately could not get hold of you, hence the delay.
Again, we apologize for the inconvenience caused and hope nevertheless to see you again on our website in the future.
Kind regards,
The Clicktransfer team.

Dear Sandeep,
Thank you for your feedback.
Most transfers through our platform are available for your recipient within minutes. 
However, this may vary by country, method of delivery you selected, and how you pay for the transaction.
Sometimes, additional factors may slow down transfer times such as: the payment entity (in recipient country) processing and opening hours, the verifying process of your bank account, additional security information, or erroneous recipient details.
We hope you will be better informed and hope to see you again on our website in the future.
Kind regards,
The Clicktransfer team.
